'''Durren Orbital''' were [[Shipyard/Legends|shipyards]] orbiting [[Durren]]. They were the home port for the ''[[Caelus]]'' and ''[[Corbantis]]''. A major [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Fleet]] installation, the station was infected by the [[Death Seed]] plague, before being cleared.

